00:20:28.110 --> 00:20:30.570 align:middle line:84%
the path of the singularity
and turning ourselves

00:20:30.570 --> 00:20:33.600 align:middle line:90%
into transhuman machines.

00:20:33.600 --> 00:20:35.400 align:middle line:84%
There's never been
a time in history

00:20:35.400 --> 00:20:39.120 align:middle line:84%
where individuals are choosing
to augment the human body as we

00:20:39.120 --> 00:20:41.110 align:middle line:90%
are now doing with technology.

00:20:41.110 --> 00:20:43.530 align:middle line:84%
With retinal implants,
cochlear implants,

00:20:43.530 --> 00:20:45.810 align:middle line:84%
all kinds of implants,
artificial organs,

00:20:45.810 --> 00:20:49.770 align:middle line:84%
we can literally pick and choose
how we want to change our looks

00:20:49.770 --> 00:20:51.810 align:middle line:84%
and how we want to change
our bodies for health

00:20:51.810 --> 00:20:53.383 align:middle line:90%
purposes or whatever reason.

00:20:53.383 --> 00:20:55.800 align:middle line:84%
And at the same time, there's
never been a time in history

00:20:55.800 --> 00:20:58.500 align:middle line:84%
where millions of
people are accessing

00:20:58.500 --> 00:21:02.100 align:middle line:84%
their organic yogic powers,
where they're digging deep.

00:21:02.100 --> 00:21:03.960 align:middle line:84%
We have millions of
people around the world,

00:21:03.960 --> 00:21:06.660 align:middle line:84%
simultaneously now,
practicing yoga.

00:21:06.660 --> 00:21:09.030 align:middle line:84%
All of this is going to
developing our highest

00:21:09.030 --> 00:21:10.620 align:middle line:90%
spiritual powers.

00:21:10.620 --> 00:21:13.650 align:middle line:84%
And perhaps there's a way
that these two perceived

00:21:13.650 --> 00:21:16.350 align:middle line:84%
or seemingly divergent
paths can converge.

00:21:16.350 --> 00:21:18.990 align:middle line:84%
Maybe there's a way that
artificial intelligence

00:21:18.990 --> 00:21:21.090 align:middle line:84%
and impacting our
flesh with technology

00:21:21.090 --> 00:21:24.300 align:middle line:84%
can somehow amplify
our spiritual powers.

00:21:24.300 --> 00:21:27.210 align:middle line:84%
I'm trying to get Silicon
Valley to get onto this path

00:21:27.210 --> 00:21:29.880 align:middle line:84%
and to utilize this
technology to develop

00:21:29.880 --> 00:21:32.880 align:middle line:84%
our spiritual powers rather
than our brain powers,

00:21:32.880 --> 00:21:35.340 align:middle line:90%
just simply because we can.

00:21:35.340 --> 00:21:37.500 align:middle line:84%
Their modus operandi
is operating

00:21:37.500 --> 00:21:39.660 align:middle line:84%
from that place where
many people operate,

00:21:39.660 --> 00:21:41.250 align:middle line:90%
the love of power.

00:21:41.250 --> 00:21:44.250 align:middle line:84%
We're developing this
technology because we can.

00:21:44.250 --> 00:21:47.790 align:middle line:84%
We're augmenting the
human body because we can.

00:21:47.790 --> 00:21:50.490 align:middle line:84%
It's not being directed
at an ultimate higher

00:21:50.490 --> 00:21:53.820 align:middle line:84%
purpose of accentuating the
potential spiritual powers

00:21:53.820 --> 00:21:56.680 align:middle line:84%
of the human body for
the power of love,

00:21:56.680 --> 00:21:59.010 align:middle line:84%
and this is the missing
conversation here.

00:21:59.010 --> 00:22:01.620 align:middle line:84%
They talk about artificially
intelligent computers

00:22:01.620 --> 00:22:04.110 align:middle line:84%
and how they're going
to be ruling over us.

00:22:04.110 --> 00:22:05.900 align:middle line:84%
But the answer is
that if we're going

00:22:05.900 --> 00:22:09.090 align:middle line:84%
to allow this to happen,
then somewhere along the way

00:22:09.090 --> 00:22:13.240 align:middle line:84%
we have to teach these
robot rulers to love us.

00:22:13.240 --> 00:22:15.030 align:middle line:84%
But here again the
problem is, how long

00:22:15.030 --> 00:22:18.150 align:middle line:84%
has humanity been trying to
learn to love one another?

00:22:18.150 --> 00:22:19.710 align:middle line:84%
Do you think in
the next five years

00:22:19.710 --> 00:22:22.500 align:middle line:84%
we can teach a robot, an
artificially intelligent robot,

00:22:22.500 --> 00:22:23.640 align:middle line:90%
to love?

00:22:23.640 --> 00:22:25.770 align:middle line:90%
I hope so.

00:22:25.770 --> 00:22:29.460 align:middle line:84%
I characterize our
situation with this battle,

00:22:29.460 --> 00:22:31.830 align:middle line:84%
if you will, these
parallel worlds

00:22:31.830 --> 00:22:35.130 align:middle line:84%
between the
technological AI and what

00:22:35.130 --> 00:22:38.680 align:middle line:84%
I call the other AI,
ascension intelligence.

00:22:38.680 --> 00:22:41.610 align:middle line:84%
You have millions of people
that are now practicing yoga,

00:22:41.610 --> 00:22:43.290 align:middle line:84%
developing their
spiritual capabilities.

00:22:43.290 --> 00:22:45.240 align:middle line:84%
And what they're
ultimately aiming for

00:22:45.240 --> 00:22:47.940 align:middle line:84%
is their own personal
ascension, which

00:22:47.940 --> 00:22:51.180 align:middle line:84%
has to do with becoming more
whole and more complete.

00:22:51.180 --> 00:22:53.407 align:middle line:84%
They use the word
perfect as well.

00:22:53.407 --> 00:22:54.990 align:middle line:84%
So we have individuals
that are trying

00:22:54.990 --> 00:22:57.360 align:middle line:84%
to become more whole
and complete and perfect

00:22:57.360 --> 00:23:00.360 align:middle line:84%
and ultimately to create a more
whole and complete and even

00:23:00.360 --> 00:23:01.950 align:middle line:90%
wholly human race.

00:23:01.950 --> 00:23:04.860 align:middle line:84%
Then on the other side you
have the gods of Silicon Valley

00:23:04.860 --> 00:23:07.200 align:middle line:84%
and Beijing and
elsewhere who are saying,

00:23:07.200 --> 00:23:11.130 align:middle line:84%
yeah, we're all about perfecting
the human race as well.

00:23:11.130 --> 00:23:14.010 align:middle line:84%
We think the human body
is far too fragile.

00:23:14.010 --> 00:23:15.540 align:middle line:84%
In fact, we think
God baked the cake

00:23:15.540 --> 00:23:17.250 align:middle line:84%
and we're going to
put the icing on it.

00:23:17.250 --> 00:23:19.770 align:middle line:84%
And the way we're going
to do that is we're

00:23:19.770 --> 00:23:22.980 align:middle line:84%
going to merge four
technologies-- bits, atoms,

00:23:22.980 --> 00:23:24.450 align:middle line:90%
neurons, and genes.

00:23:24.450 --> 00:23:27.090 align:middle line:10%
We're going to take our
computer technology or bits,

00:23:27.090 --> 00:23:29.670 align:middle line:10%
we're going to take
atoms or nanotechnology,

00:23:29.670 --> 00:23:31.417 align:middle line:10%
we're going to
take neuroscience,

00:23:31.417 --> 00:23:33.250 align:middle line:10%
and we're going to take
our genetic science,

00:23:33.250 --> 00:23:36.830 align:middle line:10%
and we're going to merge it all
into one seamless technology

00:23:36.830 --> 00:23:38.753 align:middle line:10%
that's aimed at the human body.

00:23:38.753 --> 00:23:40.670 align:middle line:84%
And we're going to create
a new layer of skin,

00:23:40.670 --> 00:23:42.770 align:middle line:84%
new artificial organs,
and we're going

00:23:42.770 --> 00:23:47.570 align:middle line:84%
to create the perfected
version of the human body.

00:23:47.570 --> 00:23:49.280 align:middle line:90%
Well, what's wrong with that?

00:23:49.280 --> 00:23:51.530 align:middle line:84%
Well, what's wrong with that
is that what we have just

00:23:51.530 --> 00:23:54.560 align:middle line:84%
described there with bits,
atoms, neurons, and genes

00:23:54.560 --> 00:23:57.260 align:middle line:84%
are what the ancients used to
call the four elements of which

00:23:57.260 --> 00:23:58.550 align:middle line:90%
our body's composed--

00:23:58.550 --> 00:24:00.810 align:middle line:90%
Earth, air, fire, and water.

00:24:00.810 --> 00:24:03.800 align:middle line:84%
But there's a fifth
element, spirit.

00:24:03.800 --> 00:24:06.680 align:middle line:84%
And that's what so many millions
of people are tapping into now.

00:24:06.680 --> 00:24:08.630 align:middle line:10%
They're tapping
into their spirit,

00:24:08.630 --> 00:24:12.030 align:middle line:10%
to their true human nature,
to develop themselves.

00:24:12.030 --> 00:24:14.130 align:middle line:84%
And so the question
then becomes,

00:24:14.130 --> 00:24:16.910 align:middle line:84%
is it possible
for spirit to come

00:24:16.910 --> 00:24:20.120 align:middle line:84%
into the technological
realm, and vise versa,

00:24:20.120 --> 00:24:22.328 align:middle line:84%
can the technology come
into the spiritual realm?

00:24:22.328 --> 00:24:23.870 align:middle line:84%
And this is what
we're in the process

00:24:23.870 --> 00:24:26.330 align:middle line:90%
of discovering right now.

00:24:26.330 --> 00:24:28.407 align:middle line:10%
As I look at the
world situation,

00:24:28.407 --> 00:24:30.740 align:middle line:10%
and you look at the governments
and how they have indeed

00:24:30.740 --> 00:24:35.660 align:middle line:10%
suppressed our natural
yogic or spiritual abilities

00:24:35.660 --> 00:24:39.860 align:middle line:10%
and now are actively promoting
artificial intelligence,

00:24:39.860 --> 00:24:42.410 align:middle line:10%
in June of 2017,
for the first time,

00:24:42.410 --> 00:24:46.072 align:middle line:10%
the United Nations actually put
together a conference in Sweden

00:24:46.072 --> 00:24:48.530 align:middle line:10%
where they brought together
the top artificial intelligence

00:24:48.530 --> 00:24:50.660 align:middle line:10%
researchers and
posed the question,

00:24:50.660 --> 00:24:52.490 align:middle line:10%
how can we use
artificial intelligence

00:24:52.490 --> 00:24:54.783 align:middle line:10%
to promote the United
Nations agenda?

00:24:54.783 --> 00:24:56.450 align:middle line:10%
Well, what is the
United Nations agenda?

00:24:56.450 --> 00:25:00.260 align:middle line:10%
Well, it's called
Agenda 2030, UN 2030.

00:25:00.260 --> 00:25:05.370 align:middle line:10%
They want the elimination of all
borders, no genders, no races.

00:25:05.370 --> 00:25:09.150 align:middle line:10%
You will simply identify
yourself as an earthling.

00:25:09.150 --> 00:25:14.370 align:middle line:84%
Not a white, male, American
earthling, in my case, simply

00:25:14.370 --> 00:25:15.540 align:middle line:90%
an earthling.

00:25:15.540 --> 00:25:18.060 align:middle line:84%
The only way that they
can make that happen

00:25:18.060 --> 00:25:21.390 align:middle line:84%
is through the
globalization of technology,

00:25:21.390 --> 00:25:24.720 align:middle line:84%
and this is why you see the
United Nations promoting

00:25:24.720 --> 00:25:29.040 align:middle line:84%
artificial intelligence now
as a way forward for humanity.

00:25:29.040 --> 00:25:30.180 align:middle line:90%
Well, wait a minute.

00:25:30.180 --> 00:25:33.090 align:middle line:84%
What happened to the spiritual
capability of humanity?

00:25:33.090 --> 00:25:35.340 align:middle line:84%
Why not uniting the
human race around

00:25:35.340 --> 00:25:38.250 align:middle line:84%
its deep spiritual
capabilities that reaches

00:25:38.250 --> 00:25:40.560 align:middle line:90%
across all religious spectrum?

00:25:40.560 --> 00:25:43.140 align:middle line:84%
Why not dig deep into
our true spiritual power

00:25:43.140 --> 00:25:44.370 align:middle line:90%
as the solution?

00:25:44.370 --> 00:25:46.380 align:middle line:84%
It seems like what we're
seeing from the highest

00:25:46.380 --> 00:25:48.690 align:middle line:84%
levels of government, beginning
with the UN and the US

00:25:48.690 --> 00:25:50.870 align:middle line:84%
government, even
the European Union,

00:25:50.870 --> 00:25:53.520 align:middle line:84%
they're devoting billions
of dollars of research

00:25:53.520 --> 00:25:57.300 align:middle line:84%
on how to augment the human body
with technology rather than how

00:25:57.300 --> 00:25:59.940 align:middle line:84%
to enhance the human body
through our spiritual

00:25:59.940 --> 00:26:00.780 align:middle line:90%
capabilities.

00:26:00.780 --> 00:26:02.850 align:middle line:90%
And that's what has to change.

00:26:02.850 --> 00:26:04.590 align:middle line:84%
And it's all the
individuals who wish

00:26:04.590 --> 00:26:07.380 align:middle line:84%
to see us develop ourselves
spiritually that now need

00:26:07.380 --> 00:26:09.810 align:middle line:84%
to stand up and
tell our government

00:26:09.810 --> 00:26:12.000 align:middle line:84%
leaders and our world
leaders that we're not

00:26:12.000 --> 00:26:14.520 align:middle line:84%
going to choose the
artificial intelligence route.

00:26:14.520 --> 00:26:17.520 align:middle line:84%
We want to take the
ascension intelligence route.

00:26:17.520 --> 00:26:19.960 align:middle line:84%
Elon Musk in his warning
to the world said,

00:26:19.960 --> 00:26:22.200 align:middle line:84%
what we are doing with
artificial intelligence

