00:27:02.440 --> 00:27:05.770 align:middle line:84%
And so, again, Musk says
we're summoning the demon.

00:27:05.770 --> 00:27:09.155 align:middle line:84%
So the answer to me is,
let's summon the angels then.

00:27:09.155 --> 00:27:11.700 align:middle line:10%
Let's summon the angels
within us in order

00:27:11.700 --> 00:27:13.980 align:middle line:10%
to combat the
demon, or find a way

00:27:13.980 --> 00:27:18.420 align:middle line:10%
to keep the demon in the box,
and find a way to utilize it

00:27:18.420 --> 00:27:21.150 align:middle line:10%
and communicate with it
to where we can utilize it

00:27:21.150 --> 00:27:28.180 align:middle line:10%
positively rather than unleash a
runaway technology on humanity.

00:27:28.180 --> 00:27:30.460 align:middle line:10%
Right now we don't
have a say other

00:27:30.460 --> 00:27:32.680 align:middle line:10%
than we utilize this technology.

