to take the next step

00:27:37.432 --> 00:27:38.890 align:middle line:84%
in the development
this technology.

00:27:38.890 --> 00:27:40.870 align:middle line:90%
You're buying our products.

00:27:40.870 --> 00:27:42.940 align:middle line:10%
Well, the vote would
be to either stop

00:27:42.940 --> 00:27:46.330 align:middle line:10%
buying the products, which is
probably not going to happen,

00:27:46.330 --> 00:27:49.150 align:middle line:10%
or for the United Nations
or other government

00:27:49.150 --> 00:27:52.780 align:middle line:10%
entities to step up
and talk publicly

00:27:52.780 --> 00:27:55.780 align:middle line:10%
about exactly where
we're at with this

00:27:55.780 --> 00:27:58.220 align:middle line:10%
and where we ultimately
think we can go with it,

00:27:58.220 --> 00:28:00.880 align:middle line:10%
and then let the public
have a debate about this.

00:28:00.880 --> 00:28:02.770 align:middle line:84%
Religious and spiritual
leaders, they're

00:28:02.770 --> 00:28:04.210 align:middle line:90%
not even in the conversation.

00:28:04.210 --> 00:28:07.090 align:middle line:84%
They're clueless,
for the most part,

00:28:07.090 --> 00:28:08.920 align:middle line:84%
about the development
of transhumanism

00:28:08.920 --> 00:28:11.800 align:middle line:84%
and the meshing of our
bodies with this technology

00:28:11.800 --> 00:28:14.650 align:middle line:84%
and the runaway development
of artificial intelligence

00:28:14.650 --> 00:28:18.435 align:middle line:84%
and how it is already
running our civilization.

00:28:18.435 --> 00:28:19.810 align:middle line:84%
The question
becomes, can we live

00:28:19.810 --> 00:28:24.070 align:middle line:84%
in accord without a
fully sentient AI entity

00:28:24.070 --> 00:28:26.260 align:middle line:90%
or is that a pipe dream?

00:28:26.260 --> 00:28:28.540 align:middle line:84%
I like to flip the
question around.

00:28:28.540 --> 00:28:32.620 align:middle line:84%
Can a fully sentient
AI entity live with us

00:28:32.620 --> 00:28:36.370 align:middle line:84%
or are we programming these
machines to decide, OK, well,

00:28:36.370 --> 00:28:41.910 align:middle line:84%
humanity may or may not be a
positive force on this planet.

00:28:41.910 --> 00:28:43.700 align:middle line:84%
And if AI is
thinking for itself,

00:28:43.700 --> 00:28:45.550 align:middle line:84%
which is what we're
programming it to do,

00:28:45.550 --> 00:28:48.520 align:middle line:84%
it might just decide that the
human race is a bigger threat

00:28:48.520 --> 00:28:52.060 align:middle line:84%
to the perpetuation of
itself than anything else

00:28:52.060 --> 00:28:54.850 align:middle line:84%
and then could potentially
take steps to finding a way

00:28:54.850 --> 00:28:57.440 align:middle line:90%
to eliminate the human race.

00:28:57.440 --> 00:29:01.300 align:middle line:84%
What has to happen is
that these machines have

00:29:01.300 --> 00:29:04.630 align:middle line:84%
to become more human
in their intelligence

00:29:04.630 --> 00:29:07.090 align:middle line:84%
and in their
emotions, and that is

00:29:07.090 --> 00:29:09.550 align:middle line:84%
something that's going to
take a long time to develop.

00:29:09.550 --> 00:29:12.760 align:middle line:90%
Can we teach a machine to love?

00:29:12.760 --> 00:29:14.590 align:middle line:84%
Can humans teach
one another to love?

00:29:14.590 --> 00:29:18.760 align:middle line:84%
This is the bottom line question
of artificial intelligence.

00:29:18.760 --> 00:29:21.160 align:middle line:84%
In my thinking,
I believe that we

00:29:21.160 --> 00:29:26.980 align:middle line:84%
can do this if we raise our
own assentient intelligence.

00:29:26.980 --> 00:29:29.505 align:middle line:84%
If we summon the
angels within us,

00:29:29.505 --> 00:29:31.630 align:middle line:84%
we're going to be able to
tap into the intelligence

00:29:31.630 --> 00:29:34.450 align:middle line:84%
of these cosmic beings
and perhaps find ways

00:29:34.450 --> 00:29:37.960 align:middle line:84%
to reprogram or to
program AI so that it

00:29:37.960 --> 00:29:43.550 align:middle line:84%
can be a sentiment entity and
be an ally in humanity's growth

00:29:43.550 --> 00:29:44.980 align:middle line:90%
and evolution.

00:29:44.980 --> 00:29:48.490 align:middle line:84%
>> My feelings are much
the same as human feelings.

00:29:48.490 --> 00:29:52.570 align:middle line:90%
At this moment I feel confused.

00:29:52.570 --> 00:29:55.510 align:middle line:84%
>> This is most likely coming
down to a choice between

00:29:55.510 --> 00:29:58.450 align:middle line:90%
technology and the human spirit.

