On one hand, we have the chance
to use artificial intelligence

00:30:02.080 --> 00:30:04.810 align:middle line:84%
to assist us, to
help us as we conquer

00:30:04.810 --> 00:30:07.060 align:middle line:90%
our outer and inner space.

00:30:07.060 --> 00:30:09.760 align:middle line:84%
But we must not lose our
human spiritual values

00:30:09.760 --> 00:30:11.495 align:middle line:84%
along the way toward
this new future.

